    q: "Do you do warranty service on Sub-Zero?",
    a: "Yes. We are part of the Sub-Zero authorized service network. We process warranty claims through Sub-Zero authorized procedures, use OEM parts, and document service for warranty preservation. General appliance repair without authorized status often violates warranty terms and uses incorrect parts. Sub-Zero authorized service network membership is a critical trust signal for premium-brand owners.",
