  {
    q: "Do you service Sub-Zero in Bel Air, Beverly Hills, Hidden Hills, Pacific Palisades, Malibu?",
    a: "Yes. These premium home neighborhoods are concentrated Sub-Zero installations because the brand defines premium kitchen architecture in LA. Same-day service in most LA County areas. Beverly Hills, Bel Air, Hidden Hills, Pacific Palisades, and Malibu are core territories for our Sub-Zero authorized service work.",
