      <li>Refrigerator drawers (UC-24R, UC-24F, 700-Series UC)</li>
      <li>All Sub-Zero refrigerator + freezer column configurations</li>
      <li>All EPA-permitted refrigerants (R-22 legacy, R-134a most common, R-600a newer green models with R-600a awareness)</li>
