<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">Pricing</p>
    <h2>Sub-Zero repair costs.</h2>

    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $89 (residential tier), waived with repair. OEM Sub-Zero parts via the authorized service network. Standard 2 to 5 day parts ship. Premium pricing reflects the OEM-only requirement (no aftermarket of consequence exists for Sub-Zero).</p>

    <table class="price-table">
