    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Sub-Zero authorized service network.</strong> Critical for warranty preservation. Authorized service uses correct procedures, correct parts, and warranty-compliant documentation. General handyman service on Sub-Zero often violates warranty terms.</li>
