      <li><strong>Replace-vs-repair honesty.</strong> A 15 to 20 year-old Sub-Zero almost always favors repair. Cabinet outlasts components by decades. Replacement cost runs $14,000 to $30,000+ plus custom cabinet refit.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus BBB A+.</strong> Verifiable with the state and the bureau.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, Orange County, Ventura.</strong> Eight branches mean tight response time.</li>
      <li><strong>24/7 phone answering, no emergency surcharge.</strong> $89 residential diagnostic anytime.</li>
